AS Kigali yegukanye Igikombe cy'Amahoro

AS Kigali ni yo yegukanye Igikombe cy'Amahoro cy'uyu mwaka nyuma yo gutsinda Kiyovu Sports ibitego 2-1.

Ikipe y'Umujyi wa Kigali yaherukaga kwegukana iri rushanwa mu 2013.

Ni ku nshuro ya gatanu Kiyovu Sports igeze ku mukino wa nyuma w'Igikombe cy'Amahoro igatsindwa.

Tubashimire mwese twabanye kuri uyu mukino, tuzasubire ku wa Gatandatu tubagezaho imikino ya CECAFA Kagame Cup izamara ibyumweru bibiri ibera i Kigali, Huye na Rubavu.

16:34

AS Kigali yegukanye Igikombe cy'Amahoro mu bagore

Ikipe ya AS Kigali mu bagore ni yo yegukanye Igikombe cy'Amahoro mu bagore, itsinze Scandinavia igitego 1-0 mu mukino wabanje.

Umwanya wa gatatu muri iki cyiciro wakiniwe ejo hashize, Inyemera WFC itsinda Mutunda WFC ibitego 4-1.

Mu bagabo umwanya wa gatatu wegukanywe na Rayon Sports yatsinze Police FC ibitego 3-1.

16:30

Amateka ya AS Kigali

AS Kigali imaze imyaka 13 ishinzwe nyuma yo kwihuza kwa Renaissance FC na Kigali FC mu 2006, ikaba imaze kwegukana igikombe kimwe cyâ€™Amahoro mu 2013.

Les Citadins yahindutse Kigali, FC yegukanye Igikombe cy'Amahoro mu 2001.

Amateka ya Kiyovu Sports

Kiyovu Sports imaze imyaka 58 ibayeho nyuma yo kwemezwa nâ€™iteka rya minisitiri mu 1961 ndetse imaze kwegukana shampiyona yâ€™u Rwanda inshuro eshanu zirimo iyo mu 1990 yatwaye idatsinzwe. 16:19

Ikaze kuri Stade ya Kigali i Nyamirambo

IGIHE ibahaye ikaze kuri Stade ya Kigali i Nyamirambo hagiye kubera umukino wa nyuma w'Igikombe cy'Amahoro hagati ya AS Kigali na Kiyovu Sports.

Ni ku nshuro ya mbere aya makipe yombi afashwa n'Umujyi wa Kigali, ahuriye ku mukino wa nyuma w'Igikombe cy'Amahoro.

AS Kigali yageze ku mukino wa nyuma isezereye Rayon Sports muri 1/2 mu gihe Kiyovu Sports yakuyemo Police FC.

Umukino nyir'izina uteganyijwe mukanya saa 17:00.
